attributes.visitorReview: This would make a nice souvenir
It’s so cute! My grand-aunt used to have one like this. She was obsessed with it! Literally, obsessed. Was carted off to an asylum with it.
Oooh, creepy! Is this from a horror film set?
Did you know there’s blood on this one? I want a discount!
I don’t know how it got into my purse. I could swear it winked and whispered ‘Take me home’. You’ve heard it too, right?
This belongs to my three-year-old! A crazy old lady took it away from him in the park the other day. How did it end up in here?
Wow. I always wanted to blow something so… twisted. Can I?
My neighbor plays the same thing. I know because I went over to KILL HIM last night, but he never heard me knock over the damn PIANO!
Will it fit into my living room? I want my partner’s parents to think I’m an intellectual when they come over.
This looks like something I could do. Probably better than most people. I mean, how hard can it be?
This would make a nice coffee table.
Hm. I wonder if you could kill a person with a bell...
This is loud and screechy. Nice! Just what I need for this neighbor of mine who bangs on my door every time I play the piano
